She is such a professional yet soft spoken.
She understood complete issue. She heard all my questions. I went to her after being treated by another doctor for a week. She helped me in one visit. No extra tests. She is a well informed doctor, experienced in her domain.

She has the touch of mother. I was comfortable to share all the details. She heard it all the patience.

I not in pain anymore after almost 1 month of treatment here and there.

I was suggested to visit Nidhi Madam by my relatives who have been treated by her. I found her to be a very warm person who listened to all my problems patiently. She explained every point in detail and answered all my queries.Her charming smile made me feel comfortable.I underwent a major surgery which was performed by madam.What impressed me the most was her genuine concern for the patients. I am extremely satisfied with her treatment and sincerely recommend Dr. Nidhi Nair to those who are seeking good healthcare.
